name: MEDALS EARNED BY ZHU ZHU ZHU
body:
Shuphahamshustrong (earned: July 18th, 2016) 
Gold Medals
* Gold hamshustrong (earned: July 20th, 2016) for her overwhelming pi-gu-niu-niu cuteness
* Gold hamshustrong (earned: July 26th, 2016) for reading the interest rate paper and collected all the notes!

Rules
* you can earn ONE platinum hamshustrong medal with TEN gold hamshustrong medals 
* you can earn ONE diamond hamshustrong medal with TEN platinum hamshustrong medals
* the awards are received TWO MONTHS after the earned date to ensure that the awardee meets the honor code of conduct during the exemplary period!
